  <source>Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate a new instrument that shines light and takes digital
      pictures of skin. The goal is to develop a technique that may enable fast and accurate
      detection of skin disorders and cancers for future clinical diagnosis and surgical use.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
